  "body": "In our production environment we have way too many topics.\r\nAnd because of that we constantly get timeouts when initializing the application\r\n(As of now the list topics operation timeout is fixed at 10 seconds)\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/36351d4412da3a529ed2c020b0fd6ad2a8145bcb/extensions/kafka-streams/runtime/src/main/java/io/quarkus/kafka/streams/runtime/KafkaStreamsProducer.java#L327\r\n\r\nWe currently do not use the validation if the topic was created or not. It would be very helpful for us if we could:\r\n1. Completely disable this verification\r\n2. Increase the timeout of the operation\r\n\r\nBecause of this issue , we are unable to use the quarkus-kafka-streams extension :cry: \r\n",
